high_descs: walk to the countertop in the kitchen
pick up the spatula from the counter
Put the spatula in the sink and fill the sink with water.
pick up the spatula from the sink
Bring the spatula from the drawer to the living room.
Put the spatula in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Get the spatula from the drawer.

high_descs: exit the bedroom to reach the countertop in the kitchen room.
Take the spatula from the kitchen table.
The spatula moves towards the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, clean the spatula off.
Take back the spatula in the drawer.
Place the spatula inside the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Clean the spatula on the table and place spatula inside the drawer

high_descs: Walk to the doorway on your left, then hang a right and walk to the countertop
Pick up the spatula on the countertop
Walk to the sink on your right
Put the spatula in the sink, wash it off, take it back up
Turn around, go between the coffee table and sofa, head towards the drawer next to the sofa to your right
Put the spatula in the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula in a drawer
